      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How to read this:\n\nEach table = an Excel sheet\nEach row = one record\nArrows = relationships\n\n1:N means \"one to many\".\nOne game can have many loans\n(borrowed multiple times).\nOne member can have many loans\n(borrow multiple games).\n\nAll of this lives in a single\nfile: refugio.db",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
